I think most members of the public would say, “</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Hang it, I’</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">m not getting involved in this.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">There are so many different avenues.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">”</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> I am not saying that the average member of</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> the public is not intelligent—</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">clearly</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">, they are—</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">but</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> with all these bodies ranged across the spectrum</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> it is extremely complicated and confusing, is it not?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 10pt 14.2pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">Stephen Green</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">: </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">It is incredibly complicated and I have to say, until I start</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ed</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> doing </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">my </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">research to apply for this job, I had no idea of the vast maze of ombudsman sch